ent-workflow Specification\\n\\n## Purpose\\nTracks the lifecycle of each client's annual tax filing as a per-client, per-tax-year engagement. Supports a five-state machine (START ŌåÆ IN_PROCESSING ŌåÆ PENDING_CLIENT_REVIEW ŌåÆ SUBMIT_TO_CRA ŌåÆ COMPLETED) with any-to-ŌĆ”","sessionId":"10e14017-2f3e-4428-9177-17ccd5eb1fb1","subtitle":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/specs/client-engagement-workflow/spec.md\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T23:25:10.055Z","title":"Read","type":"file_read"},"sessionId":"10e14017-2f3e-4428-9177-17ccd5eb1fb1","type":"compressed"},"obs_mqwzn2lo_ee3ff844ac62":{"observation":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/engagement-name-note/proposal.md"],"id":"obs_mqwzn2lo_ee3ff844ac62","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"content\":\"---\\nDate: 2026-06-27\\nChange: engagement-name-note\\nRequirements: requirements.md\\n---\\n\\n## Why\\n\\nA client can have more than one business ŌĆö a personal tax return and a corporation, for example ŌĆö but the system currently enforces one engagement per client per tax year, making it impossible to track both filings independently. This change removes that constraint and gives each engagŌĆ”","sessionId":"10e14017-2f3e-4428-9177-17ccd5eb1fb1","subtitle":"{\"content\":\"---\\nDate: 2026-06-27\\nChange: engagement-name-note\\nRequirements: requirements.md\\n---\\n\\n## Why\\n\\nA clieŌĆ”","timestamp":"2026-06-27T23:25:31.466Z","title":"Write","type":"file_write"},"sessionId":"10e14017-2f3e-4428-9177-17ccd5eb1fb1","type":"compressed"},"obs_mqwzn5jc_e328cdb15767":{"observation":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwzn5jc_e328cdb15767","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"command\":\"openspec status --change engagement-name-note --json\",\"description\":\"Check status after writing proposal\"} | {\"interrupted\":false,\"isImage\":false,\"noOutputExpected\":false,\"stderr\":\"\",\"stdout\":\"{\\n  \\\"chan